  "3191700": {
    "name": "鲤氏奇人异闻录",
    "steam_appid": 3191700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/2165ac47bbf3f80e271e977d5cd6b55c.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《鲤氏奇人异闻录》（以下统称“本作”）是《明日方舟》（以下统称“原作”）的同人游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作以原作角色“老鲤”为主角（本作中名为“鲤”），玩家将以“鲤”的视角展开一系列解谜探案故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作为同人作品，同人倾向为：老鲤中心，无CP，剧情向，一般向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>tips：本作剧情相对独立，即便您对《明日方舟》没有了解，也可以将本作当作一款普通的文字解谜游戏游玩！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作主要故事发生在炎国龙门，故事时间在原作主线序章（1097年）约二十年前，世界观及背景设定尽量贴近原作，但在原作基础上进行了一定的<strong>必要延展</strong>，如有错漏，敬请谅解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作登场人物中，鲤（老鲤）、老董（董阿伯）、林（鼠王林舸瑞）、魏彦吾、蔡老板（菜贩老蔡）为原作角色，由于故事发生在二十年前，本作对他们进行了少量重新演绎，OOC之处，敬请谅解；<strong>其余人物均为本作原创角色</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除“源石”及“源石技艺”相关设定外，本作所涉及的基础科学原理均与现实相符。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本作完全免费</strong>，无任何商业性质，不包含任何收费项目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作为悬疑解谜游戏，剧情涉及凶杀案件，包含少量血腥画面及血腥暴力相关的文字描写，推荐16岁以上玩家游玩，建议18岁以下玩家谨慎游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作所描写、展示的内容（包括且不限于所有画面及文字）均属艺术设计需要，不代表创作者认同、允许或鼓励作品中所提及的任何行为及立场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作属于虚构作品，作品内所有人名、组织、地点、事件等均属虚构，如有雷同，纯属巧合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/f2e4570eb52f629285031073d9b16f67.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >二十年前</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年轻的老鲤初至龙门</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被卷入一起凶案</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >案情复杂奇诡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引来龙门黑白两道重要人物关注</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为尽早脱困</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本无意招惹是非的鲤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定主动追查真凶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到真相</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一遭   究竟是</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天命难违   亦或   人定胜天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >且看他   回首处</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但思善恶   笑语   无问吉凶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/d1d524877c16c12671c78d5fd3b8a422.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本游戏中，玩家将<strong>扮演年轻时的老鲤</strong>，作为一名侦探，调查发生在龙门的数起案件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏基本形式为阅读故事（类似《明日方舟》剧情部分）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初入龙门，就从结识新朋友开始吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/a9bcc410707f995dca130c2f313d9647.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=338 /></span><strong>（游戏开始界面。达成任意结局后，可开启鉴赏模式。）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/6db22a8a3fc1ba7da4f67cfd42448a00.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=338 /></span><strong>（剧情界面。可点击对话框右侧的按钮进行多项操作，具体操作方法可参考以下“操作方式”说明。）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情推进至一定阶段时，随着“案件”发生，将出现“调查”“问询”“分析”等特殊环节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【调查】：</strong>点击特殊场景中的可调查物品，收集线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【问询】：</strong>与案件相关角色对话，收集线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【分析】：</strong>根据收集到的线索解答一系列问题，分析真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/97e007f910dae1543272b5c8e068be03.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=338 /></span><strong>（在剧情推进过程中，可随时查看已经收集到的线索。）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在剧情推进过程中，还会出现不同的<strong>“分支选项”</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据案情分析正确与否、以及对分支选项的选择情况，目前共规划<strong>8种可达成结局</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/95028957947809d008571b380be09777.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=338 /></span><strong>（序章开始界面。敬请期待鲤的探案故事！(*^▽^*) // ）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/f3dd2eeecc3845ceb62fe685de49beae.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标左键or空格键or回车键：确认/进行对话 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标右键：返回/隐藏对话框</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标滚轮向上：浏览历史记录</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标滚轮向下：进行对话</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话框右上角按钮功能：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击“自”按钮：自动对话/自动运行游戏；单击画面任意位置可解除自动运行</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击“速”按钮：快速跳过对话；单击画面任意位置可解除快速跳过</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击“储”按钮：进入存储界面，可进行存档</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击“取”按钮：进入读档界面，可进行读档</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击“证”按钮（白色按钮）：进入线索界面，查看目前已获得的线索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击“设”按钮：进入系统设置界面，可调整显示模式、音量、跳过对话条件等内容；可退回开始界面或关闭游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击右下角“眼睛”按钮：隐藏对话框</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击右下角“箭头”按钮：浏览历史记录</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191700/extras/7a8abf7f8eed5f428246219954f4f5b5.avif?t=1729823109\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作/发行：顽童计划</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主催/制作人：茶叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏使用THE NVL Maker制作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序：茶叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >编剧 · 撰稿：茶叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与撰稿 · 第一章：林景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人物立绘美术：白叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >线索图标美术：白叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG · 剧情插画：白叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG · 剧情插画/GUEST：猫切希尔郡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查环节美术：未雨喵喵</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景美术 · 绘制部分：未雨喵喵</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景美术 · 照片改绘部分：风灵</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景美术 · 照片转制部分：茶叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >照片来源：实地拍摄（茶叶）、pxhere（符合网站使用规约）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI美术：茶叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐 · 授权曲库：麋鹿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音效来源于以下网站 · 均符合使用规约：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小森平的免费下载音效</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ザ·マッチメイカァズ</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱给网</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他杂务：茶叶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >============================</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2024 年 10 月</p>",
